@[basesystem step]
In this step, you will unpack and install the basesystem chroot image to your target partitions.

enchantment:
  @[enchantment install basesystem]

manually:
  @[tar -xf /system.tar.xz -C "$ENCHANT_TARGET"]

If all goes well, you will have a very minimal base system that you can now play around in.

When you are ready, type @[next].
